with you and the cameras

00:00:26.690 --> 00:00:28.880 align:middle line:10%
and to say hello to
all your audience.

00:00:28.880 --> 00:00:31.940 align:middle line:84%
>>LILOU: Well, thank you for
coming all the way from Mexico.

00:00:31.940 --> 00:00:34.145 align:middle line:10%
Because we're here in
this beautiful paradise.

00:00:34.145 --> 00:00:35.645 align:middle line:84%
And I'm happy that
I flew to France.

00:00:35.645 --> 00:00:38.850 align:middle line:84%
And here we are having this
conversation on consciousness,

00:00:38.850 --> 00:00:40.860 align:middle line:90%
this juicy conversation.

00:00:40.860 --> 00:00:42.200 align:middle line:10%
Because you're an author.

00:00:42.200 --> 00:00:43.553 align:middle line:10%
You were a TV host, too.

00:00:43.553 --> 00:00:44.720 align:middle line:10%
I mean, you had what a life.

00:00:44.720 --> 00:00:45.775 align:middle line:10%
Tell us about your background.

00:00:45.775 --> 00:00:46.730 align:middle line:10%
>>ROMERO: Oh, yes.

00:00:46.730 --> 00:00:50.840 align:middle line:10%
Well, you know, life jumps
in a very unexpected way.

00:00:50.840 --> 00:00:53.770 align:middle line:10%
